articles.title: Dead pig found at home of New Jersey rabbi: police
articles.description: Detectives in Lakewood are looking into the dead animal left at the Treetop Lane home of a rabbi on Saturday as an apparent bias crime, police told The Post early Monday.
articles.content:
A dead pig was left on the doorstep of a New Jersey rabbi over the Jewish Sabbath — an incident that’s being probed as an apparent bias crime, police told The Post on Monday.
